Product name: Ladies Claddagh Ring
Description:
This is a claddagh ring made in sold sterling silver, solid 10k gold, solid 14k gold, solid 18k gold or Platinum.  This ring is a traditional Irish ring with many myths and legends surrounding it.  One of the best known is that the first ring was made by a young man from Galway, Ireland who was captured by Corsican pirate and spent many years enslaved in the Middle East.  While a slave he learned gold smithing.  When the Irish king negeotiated for the release of the slaves, he returned to Galway and married the girl who had waited all the years for him.  He made her a claddagh for a wedding ring with hands to symbolize friendship, a crown to symbolize loyalty and fidelity and a heart to symbolize eternal love.  
According to Irish author Colin Murphy, the way in which a Claddagh ring was worn with the intention of conveying the wearer's relationship status:
On the right hand with the point of the heart toward the fingertips, the wearer is single and may be looking for love. (This is most commonly the case when a young woman has first received the ring from a relative, unless she is already engaged.)
On the right hand with the point of the heart toward the wrist, the wearer is in a relationship.
On the left hand with the point of the heart toward the fingertips, the wearer is engaged.
On the left hand with the point of the heart toward the wrist, the wearer is married.
While puzzle rings are our specialty, we offer a wide range of non-puzzle rings in a variety of motifs. We carry rings for animal lovers, motorcycle enthusiasts, horse aficionados, and many other styles and interests. They are heavy, solid rings.
We make over 100 designs of puzzle rings, gimmal rings, féde rings, chain rings and wedding puzzle rings drawing from the traditions of Turkey, Saudi Arabia, Persia, and Europe, and our own modern variations. 
Each ring is handcrafted in our workshop in middle Tennessee, drawing on our own family tradition which is nearing its 70th anniversary. Tacey makes all items by hand with some help from part-time employees.
SHIPPING:  Orders generally ship within a week, and sooner if we have an item in stock.  We now offer you the opportunity to choose the method of shipping you prefer.  When you check out, a drop down box will offer you the various shipping prices and give you the time each should take to get to you.  This shipping time is in addition to the 3 - 5 business days it takes to make your item to order.  
NOTE FOR INTERNATIONAL CUSTOMERS:  If your custom regulators require duties or taxes, you are responsible. We recommend purchasing insurance, as we are not responsible for lost or damaged packages.  WE CANNOT GUARANTEE SHIPPING TIMES FOR INTERNATIONAL ORDERS.
Available in 10k, 14k & 18k gold, platinum and mixed precious metals, and with or without semi-precious and precious stones. Our .925 Sterling silver is nickel-free and tarnish resistant.  All men’s puzzle rings are heavier than ladies rings in the same style and priced accordingly.
Rings can be made in any size.  If you wear an unusual size that is not listed, such as a larger or smaller ring, please contact us for prices and manufacturing time.  Most items can be completed within a week.  
All of our jewelry is handcrafted, so expect some slight variation among pieces of jewelry even of the same style.
We welcome custom orders and special projects and would be happy to list a special order, reserved just for you if you prefer gold, platinum or mixed precious metals. Just convo us for prices.

This box also comes with a metal latch latch to keep the box closed, if you keep the latch up, you will be able to fit a small lock on the box. This is a shabby chic looking card/ keepsake box and is offered in white or a rustic driftwood in color. Please keep in mind that these do have a rustic appearance and all will have their own characteristic, no two boxes will look exactly the same. You will get a one of a kind piece! There is a card slot opening in the top part of this box for easy insert of your wedding cards. This card box makes a wonderful wedding decor item and a great keepsake for remembering your special day. This also makes for a great bridal shower gift for your bride to be or baby shower gift for the mommy to be.

We only use the listed processing times in each listing, we will not honor a date you leave in the notes.
